1. install jasmine.js

        npm install jasmine

2. install karma.js

        npm install karma --save-dev
        npm install karma-jasmine karma-chrome-launcher --save-dev

3. Initialize karma

        ./node_modules/karma/bin/karma init my.conf.js

4. After answering karma's questions, start karma with

        ./node_modules/karma/bin/karma start my.conf.js
